<h1>New message on HopHub</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @entry.name %>,</p>

<p><strong><%= @name %></strong> has sent you a message on HopHub, and this is what they said:</p>

<div class="quote"><%= @text %></div>

<p>You can reply to this email to answer directly to <%= @name %>.</p>

<p>Your offer for the event "<strong><%= @entry.event.name %></strong>" is still active and visible here:</p>

<p><a href="<%= event_entry_url(@entry.event, @entry) %>" class="button">View your offer</a></p>

<p>In case your offer is no longer up to date or relevant, please use the secret link from your confirmation email to edit or delete it.</p>

<p>Happy sharing, you are awesome!</p>

<p class="signoff">Kind regards from the HopHub platform.</p>
